---
// Static redirect - instant via meta refresh + JS fallback
---
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0;url=/en/" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="/en/" />
    <title>Redirecting…</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <script>window.location.replace('/en/');</script>
  </body>
</html>
